<div class="container py-5">
    <h2 class="mb-4 text-success fw-bold">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="fs-5">We’d love to hear from you. Reach us through the following:</p>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h4>📍 Address</h4>
            <p>Khati Supper Shop<br />H# Shop 104,Ground floor,<br />Backword Number 3 gate,HatirPool,Shahbag,Jabin Tower<br />Dhaka-1000, Bangladesh</p>

            <h4>📞 Phone</h4>
            <p>+880 1747732408</p>
            <p>+880 1400992069</p>

